NAME
    Perinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::ShowArgsAfterValidation - (DEPRECATED)
    Patch Perinci::CmdLine::Lite's hook_before_action() to show arguments
    after validation

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of
    Perinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::ShowArgsAfterValidation (from Perl
    distribution Perinci-CmdLine-Lite-Patch-ShowArgsAfterValidation),
    released on 2020-10-16.

SYNOPSIS
     % PERL5OPT=-MPerinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::ShowArgsAfterValidation yourscript.pl ...

DESCRIPTION
    DEPRECATION NOTICE. Deprecated in favor of
    Perinci::CmdLine::Plugin::DumpArgs.

    This patch can be used for debugging.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Perinci-CmdLine-Lite-Patch-ShowArgsAfterVa
    lidation>.

SOURCE
